&lt;Cato Corp> said it filed withthe Securities and Exchange Commission for an initial publicoffering of 2.7 mln shares of stock.    The company said the offering is expected to be made in midor late April at a price of 13 to 15 dlrs a share.    It said Shearson Lehman Bros Inc and Interstate SecuritiesCorp are managing the offering. The company is selling 680,000shares, and 2,020,000 shares are being sold by stockholders.    Proceeds from the offering will used to fund growth andincreasing levels of inventory and receivables. The companyoperates 475 women's specialty stores in 20 states. Reuter&#3;